# Screenshot Output Directory

This directory contains UI/UX documentation screenshots.

## Generated Files

Screenshots are generated by running:
```bash
python3 assets/capture_screenshots_simple.py
```

## Structure

- `01_light_theme_main.png` - Market Pulse (light theme)
- `02_dark_theme_main.png` - Market Pulse (dark theme)
- `03_design_system_light.png` - Design System Gallery (light theme)
- `04_design_system_dark.png` - Design System Gallery (dark theme)

## Notes

- Screenshots are full-page captures at 1920x1080 resolution
- Generated from Streamlit app running on localhost:8501
- See `docs/SCREENSHOTS.md` for capture instructions
